				<h2 id="content-distribution">Content Distribution</h2>
				<p>
					MOFILM is one of the worlds fastest growing film making communities, currently exceeding
					100,000 creative individuals, studios and agencies.
				</p>

				<p class="alignCenter"><img src="{$themeimages}/business/business-distribution-logos.png" alt="Logos" /></p>

				<p>
					During the past three years our Film Festivals have attracted entries from talented
					individuals across the world, many going on to win other film festivals and high acclaim
					within the film industry. In order to enter a film for submission to our film festival
					we simply ask that the content be less than 5 minutes in length and assigned to one of our
					five genres, Comedy, Horror&amp;Sci-fi, Animation, Drama or Documentaries. These are the only
					limitations we set.
				</p>
				<p>
					Once a film has been submitted to our film festival, MOFILM hold the non-exclusive rights
					for digital distribution on a global basis. As can be seen by the standard of our
					finalists, the bar is set high and year-on-year we are amazed by the quality of short films
					that we receive, as such we have constructed a distribution network to share our content with
					as many people as possible.
				</p>
				<p>
					MOFILM work with Mobile Network Operators, Content Distributors, ISP&rsquo;s, Broadcaster,
					Brands and Agencies in order to maximise our reach. MOFILM content is currently licensed
					to 32 Mobile Network Operators in 23 countries however the list is increasing.
				</p>
				<p>
					Our Direct to Consumer offering allows access from any mobile internet browser worldwide,
					MOFILM recognise the handsets trying to access our mobile portal and deliver the correct
					application accordingly. MOFILM have also developed handset specific applications to be
					distributed using iPhone Applications Store, Android Market, and Blackberry Boutique.
				</p>
				<p>
					Find out more about MOFILM, if you are a mobile network operator, content distributor, film
					maker or even interested in showing our films during transatlantic flights please do not
					hesitate to email us at <a href="mailto:content@mofilm.com">content@mofilm.com</a> or hit one
					of the links at the top of the page for more specific information.
				</p>
				<p><a href="#top" target="_top">Back to Top</a></p>

				<hr />

				<h2 id="mobile-network-operators">Mobile Network Operators</h2>
				<p>
					MOFILM offer Mobile Network Operators the opportunity to showcase some of the latest, individual
					and highly creative mobile film content available.
				</p>

				<p class="alignCenter"><img src="{$themeimages}/business/business-distribution-logos2.png" alt="Logos" /></p>

				<p>
					Working to a maximum duration of 5 minutes our creative&rsquo;s are challenged to produce
					compelling and engaging short films for mobile consumers. Please take a moment to check out some
					of the finalists from this years film festival in order to gauge the quality of content that we
					deliver.
				</p>
				<p>
					MOFILM have employed mobile experts with the skills and experience in running mobile content
					from pure delivery through to managing dedicated portals for some of the worlds largest mobile
					network operators, we not only understand your requirements and needs but as importantly, those
					of your consumers.
				</p>
				<p>
					Genres range from; Comedy, Horror &amp; Sci-fi, Animation, Drama or Documentaries. MOFILM can
					also provide exclusive content from individual pieces through to made-for-mobile series. Due to
					the wide range of expertise from within our film making community we relish the challenge to find
					the content that you require.
				</p>

				<h3>We can provide MOFILM content in a number of ways:</h3>
				
				<h4>Pure content delivery</h4>
				<p>
					Content can be taken from our platform or delivered to you in the format specified.
				</p>
				<p>
					From our ftp site or delivered to your content requirements by the MOFILM platform, MOFILM
					delivers content in multiple digital formats, ready for mobile, online and broadcast. We
					currently provide Free-to-Consumer content that can by funded by mobile advertising, or
					licensed from MOFILM for a monthly management fee basis.
				</p>

				<h4>Dedicated Channels</h4>
				<p>
					MOFILM can create a dedicated Film, Comedy, Animation or MOFILM channel. MOFILM provide a
					fully managed service delivering content via applications such as Android Market, iPhone,
					Blackberry, Java and Mobile Internet sites.
				</p>

				<h4>Run your own film festival!</h4>
				<p>
					The MOFILM platform designed to manage our global film festival and can be licensed by you to
					use as part of your own film festival. Get your consumers to create their own short films
					and be able to view and vote for each other&rsquo;s content. MOFILM is the natural partner to
					choose to fully manage your very own mobile film festival.
				</p>

				<h4>Applications</h4>
				<p>
					MOFILM have been invited by handset manufacturers such as Blackberry to created Mobile
					Applications specifically for their handset market.
				</p>
				<p>
					MOFILM can create applications to your specifications. Applications are becoming more prominent
					with consumers displaying a positive change in behaviour and willingness to discover the routes
					to more content within their handsets.<br />With proven experience in this market, MOFILM can
					design an application for you to meet yours and your consumer needs.
				</p>

				<h4>Managed Mobile Internet service</h4>
				<p>
					By typing <a href="http://www.mofilm.com">www.mofilm.com</a> into any mobile browser you will
					experience the MOFILM MOBILE Direct to Consumer service. This is a fully managed service that
					is updated regularly with all the latest MOFILM content, and updates from a film festivals and
					creative projects. Free to Consumer our model is powered by advertising revenues. MOFILM offer
					you a fully managed service, all you need to do is to promote the site through our portal and
					to your consumers.
				</p>

				<h4>MOBILE Advertising</h4>
				<p>
					MOFILM maintains advertising partnership with leading sales houses on a global basis. MOFILM
					can provide you with mobile advertising as part of the fully managed service, enabling revenue
					streams from Free-to-Consumer content.
				</p>
				
				<h4>Exclusive Content</h4>
				<p>
					MOFILM regularly receive exclusive content and update our content partners accordingly. If you
					would like to find out more about offering exclusive content, episodicles or award winning
					films to your audience please do not hesitate to contact us and find out what we have available.
					If you have a particular requirement we can commission work on your behalf.
				</p>
				<p>
					MOFILM is based on a very versatile platform, combined with award winning content and our
					expertise we are confident that we can partner with you and work to your specific requirements.
				</p>
				<p><a href="#top" target="_top">Back to Top</a></p>

				<hr />

				<h2 id="film-makers">Film Makers</h2>
				<p>
					Get Creative, Get Noticed, Get Famous! MOFILM distribute short films globally with the largest
					distribution reach in our market. Want to work with the worlds leading brands and monetise
					your content? Comprising of multiple digital platforms including handset specific devices made
					for the iPhone, Google Android and Blackberry devices, covering in excess of 23 countries we
					showcase the finest in short film content.
				</p>
				<p>
					The MOFILM Film Festival and brand incentives have created a film making community in excess of
					100,000, with all the high quality content that we received we wanted to create a network of
					consumers that like to watch short films.
				</p>
				<p>
					The first question that we had to answer was based around discovery, how are consumers going to
					find and interact with MOFILM?
				</p>
				<p>
					Mobile phones are the ideal medium for watching our short films, with over 950 million handsets
					being sold last year alone. In many emerging territories more people have access to the mobile
					phone than they do the internet. MOBILE entertainment is growing due to handset manufacturers
					continually updating and improving on the quality of the product, larger screens and flat rate
					data tariffs along with educating consumers on how to use the mobile internet has influenced our
					success.
				</p>
				<p>
					How do we activate these consumers? MOFILM currently licenses content to 38 Mobile Network
					Operators in 23 countries, we have also created a mobile internet application to allow all
					handsets with a mobile browser to view our short films.
				</p>
				<p>
					All the consumer needs to do is to type <a href="http://www.mofilm.com">www.mofilm.com</a> into
					a mobile internet browser in order to download or stream MOFILM content.
				</p>
				<p>
					MOFILM have also created specific device applications, and continue to do so.
				</p>
				<p>
					We support iPhone Apps, Blackberry RIM applications and Android Handset Applications, we are also
					showcasing MOFILM content on NOKIA OVI and continue to work with handset manufacturers to pre
					install MOFILM content and the MOFILM MOBILE application.
				</p>
				<p>
					We monetise our content in a variety of ways, mainly we offer the service free-to-consumer with
					mobile advertising to generate revenues, we also license content and sell content at a premium
					rate. At each point you will receive 50% net revenues from your content.
				</p>
				<p>
					And we don&rsquo;t stop there. MOFILM continue to develop new ways to improve interaction between
					MOFILM and our consumers.
				</p>
				<p>
					Give your content the opportunity to be seen, give yourself the ability to create for a revenue
					generating audience to find out more please contact us...
				</p>
				<p><a href="#top" target="_top">Back to Top</a></p>

