				<h2 id="content-distributor">Content Distributor </h2>
				<p>
					MOFILM provide a valuable service for content owners who are keen to distribute their short films
					via our network of distributors.
				</p>
				<p>
					MOFILM offer Mobile Network Operators the opportunity to showcase some of the latest, individual
					and highly creative mobile film content available.
				</p>
				<p>
					Working within a 5 minute window our creative&rsquo;s are challenged to produce compelling and
					engaging short films for mobile consumers, please take a moment to check out some of the finalists
					from this years film festival in order to gauge the quality of content that we can and do deliver.
				</p>
				<p>
					MOFILM can provide localised film content supporting your country of distribution. Working on a
					global basis enables us to support a portfolio of content that will meet your specific requirements.
				</p>
				<p>
					As a content distributor MOFILM will provide you with MOFILM content on a monthly basis, or more
					frequent should you need it.
				</p>
				<p>
					MOFILM are keen to work in partnership with other content distributors, if you have a portfolio of
					short films that would fit into the MOFILM consumer experience please contact us.
				</p>
				<p>
					Our commercial terms are flexible and are dependant on your own reach and distribution capabilities.
					Below are some of the examples of our current distribution agreements:
				</p>
				
				<p>
					<strong>Monthly Licence Fee &ndash;</strong> If you are giving content away to the consumer as part
					of a promotion.
				</p>
				<p>
					<strong>Advertising Revenue Share &ndash;</strong> MOFILM currently supply a number of content
					distributors where the content is funded by banner or video pre and post roll advertising, this is
					subject to a monthly revenue guarantee defined by your distribution reach.
				</p>
				<p>
					<strong>Revenue Share &ndash;</strong> You may want to charge consumers a premium rate, or use our
					content as part of an existing channel whereby the consumer pays on a monthly basis, part of a
					package. MOFILM are happy to look at revenue shares based on a monthly revenue guarantee.
				</p>
				<p>
					<strong>Exclusive Licence &ndash;</strong> MOFILM has access to exclusive content, this can be
					used on a campaign basis or where you would like to offer your partners some of the best short
					film content available.</p>

				<p>
					MOFILM is always pleased to hear from content distributors, we are currently licensing or content
					to 23 different countries and would like to add you to our MOFILM partners.
				</p>
